        "description": "More than one thousand items from all walks of life can be guessed through the use of 61 transparent cards in Imagine, whether they're placed next to one another or superimposed. Almost everything in the world can be represented by a simplified concept &mdash; just don't speak while you're playing...<br/><br/>",
